      "instruction": "<p>While the chips are cooking, peel and chop <strong>half </strong>your <strong>red onion[s] </strong>into quarters, then separate the wedges so you end up with a pile of onion petals</p><p>Slice the <strong>remaining red onion</strong> finely</p>",
