    {
      "instruction": "<p>Soak your <strong>skewers</strong> in <strong>cold water</strong> (this prevents them from burning whilst cooking)</p><p>Combine your <strong>baharat </strong>and<strong> </strong>a drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil </strong>in a medium bowl with a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> – this is your <strong>marinade</strong></p>",
