    {
      "instruction": "<p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick with a matching lid) over a high heat with a drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil</strong></p><p>Once hot, add the <strong>chicken skewers</strong> and cook for 2 min on each side or until golden</p><p>Once golden, cover with a lid and cook for a further 3-4 min on each side or until cooked through (no pink meat!) – these are your <strong>chicken shish kebabs</strong></p>",
