    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add your<strong> tomato ketchup</strong> to a separate bowl with your <strong>chilli flakes </strong>(can't handle the heat? Go easy!)<strong> </strong>and 1 tbsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[1 1/2 tbsp] </span><span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tbsp] </span><strong>cold water</strong></p><p>Give it a good mix up – this is your <strong>chilli sauce</strong></p><p>Once the chips are almost done, remove the tray[s] from the oven and top the chips with your <strong>wholemeal pitta[s]</strong></p><p>Return the tray[s] to the oven for 3-4 min or until warmed through</p>",
